7db" style=3D"color:#d40000;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold" class=3D=
"sdf">tweeted</a></u> about it.<br/><br/>Despite the baseless nature of the=
 conspiracy
theory, Joe and Mika =E2=80=9Care petrified of retribution and of Gaetz ope=
ning an investigation into Joe and the intern,=E2=80=9D one source with kno=
wledge of their concerns said. =E2=80=9CThat&#39;s what this was about. It =
has nothing to do with ratings or Comcast. It=E2=80=99s all about fear of r=
etribution and investigation.=E2=80=9D Another source close to the matter s=
aid Joe and Mika believed that by meeting with Trump, they could assuage hi=
s potential desire for reckless payback and thus nuke any possibility of ha=
ving to endure the headlines of a Gaetz witch hunt or legal torture campaig=
n. (Reached for comment, Scarborough referred me to an MSNBC spokesperson, =
who denied this characterization of the motivations for Joe and Mika=E2=80=
