tally, Scarborough and Gaetz both represented Florida=E2=80=99s 1st congres=
sional district. <br/><br/>In his own interview with Fox News on Monday mor=
ning, Trump described his meeting with Joe and Mika as
=E2=80=9Cvery cordial,=E2=80=9D adding that =E2=80=9Cmany things were discu=
ssed, and I very much appreciated the fact that they wanted to have open co=
